WEBVTT

00:00:00.400 --> 00:00:07.293
Hey, good morning family. Praise the Lord. Thank you for joining me today. Well, glory to God.

00:00:07.294 --> 00:00:16.639
I wasn't going to do a video today, but there's things on my heart that I would like to talk about. Diana is behind the camera. Hi.

00:00:16.640 --> 00:00:54.479
And she said, "Honey, after you did that video last night and the anointing was so strong in the house and we were interceding,"she says, "it's been on my heart all day long."You know, she's Apache and about the Trail of Tears and all of it, you know, about her ancestors and the Trail of Tears and the Native Americans and the suffering that they went through, you know, and all the different things, the hardship of people.

00:00:54.480 --> 00:01:05.576
But she said, "I feel in my spirit there's something more to what you saw about the African-American population last night, Brandon, and I don't know what it is, but I'm going to start searching.

00:01:05.577 --> 00:01:50.377
I want to study because I feel the spirit of the Lord has told me there's more."And so, she was sitting on the couch and she started just, you know, my wife's very intelligent and she's over there tapping away and she goes, "Oh, I found it."She came to me and she was crying, and she said, "Brandon, I found it."She said, "Everything the Lord,"she goes, "the Lord is so strategic in timing."She goes, "Brandon, we live in Tulsa."And she said, "I just found the Tulsa race riots started on May 31st of 1921, and they went until June 1st."And she said 30 blocks of homes were burned from African-American men and women, businesses, everything.

00:01:50.378 --> 00:01:59.039
And they called it Black Wall Street. It was a wealthier part of one of the wealthiest black suburbs in America at the time.

00:01:59.040 --> 00:02:07.559
And there were 800 people that were hurt. Several—I think it was like 30, 40 people—lost their lives.

00:02:07.560 --> 00:02:17.598
36 total: 26 African-Americans and 10 white. Yep. A very tragic thing.

00:02:17.599 --> 00:02:30.559
And I just, wow, what was on, you know, when I come, you know, I let you in on something that's so private to Diana and me, our prayer time.

00:02:30.560 --> 00:02:42.296
You don't allow—it's very, for me, it's taken a learning curve for me to let people in because this is my walk that I've had since I've been 16.

00:02:42.297 --> 00:02:56.302
It's something I've developed. And when you sit at the Father's feet, He shows you what's on His heart.

00:02:56.303 --> 00:03:04.615
He shows you what's on His heart. He shows you what He's compassionate about—things that you think have been forgotten.

00:03:04.616 --> 00:03:18.521
Things like—I saw whenever I was in the spirit, I saw a rug, a big-looking rug, a throw rug, and it was being lifted up and it was used like a dustpan, and people wanted to brush all the dirt underneath it.

00:03:18.522 --> 00:03:36.391
And He said, "I'm going to take that rug up and I'm exposing the darkness, and I'm exposing the dirt underneath that rug."Brandon, the hurt, the pain is real and it still exists in a lot of people. And I'm ready to heal it. I'm ready to set these people free.

00:03:36.392 --> 00:04:01.140
But not only that, I saw Harriet Tubman, the African-American woman with the purple durag, and it was amazing, folks, is that I saw pictures of her—my son Googled her and we started looking—with purple durags just like I saw, with the white shirt, when she was doing the Underground Railroad.

00:04:01.141 --> 00:04:11.139
But they called it Black Wall Street. And if you remember last night, I kept seeing Wall Street, Wall Street, and I saw New York City.

00:04:11.140 --> 00:04:23.807
And that was how the Lord was describing to me—not about New York City, it was a type and shadow of something that He was, because I'm seeing New York being painted in front of my face.

00:04:23.808 --> 00:04:28.599
But He doesn't tell me "Tulsa Wall Street"because I wouldn't have understood.

00:04:28.600 --> 00:04:40.799
He was talking to me directly about Wall Street in New York, and it was a type and shadow of what was going on with the race riots in Tulsa, Oklahoma.

00:04:40.800 --> 00:05:19.669
And my mind was—I'm humbled that He would want to take a bald-headed white guy, come on YouTube, and want me to pray for something so precious to Him.

00:05:19.670 --> 00:06:07.932
I don't know why me, all these people. God, what He allowed me to see last night, none of you can understand it.

00:06:07.933 --> 00:06:15.999
Even the African-American people that are here right now have a glimpse of what you've heard.

00:06:16.000 --> 00:06:33.116
But I went into the depth of the heart of it in the spirit, and I could feel it in intercession.

00:06:33.117 --> 00:06:47.439
Those people in chains and the pain they felt, so much God would give me glimpses of their heart.

00:06:47.440 --> 00:06:58.833
And words can't explain to you the bondage and the hopelessness that they felt, similar to, I'm sure, what the children of Israel felt for 400 years.

00:06:58.834 --> 00:07:07.057
But people, you can read a story, you can read a novel, you can read history books. That's what I'm trying to say.

00:07:07.058 --> 00:07:20.017
You can read history books, and you can hear about this woman with the purple rag, and we all think she's great, or Rosa Parks sitting in the back of the bus.

00:07:20.017 --> 00:07:30.959
These people, we hear about them, and maybe somebody might have known them, but a story is nothing until you feel it.

00:07:30.960 --> 00:07:37.675
That's what I'm trying to tell you. The Trail of Tears, I was there in the spirit realm.

00:07:37.676 --> 00:07:41.907
I could see the children. I could see these people walking in the snow.

00:07:41.908 --> 00:07:51.580
I could see they were barefoot and their feet were blistering with frostbite walking across the land.

00:07:51.581 --> 00:08:08.735
And I could see them, and they were so—they were tied up and they were going across the land, getting taken out of their area where they lived to be taken to Oklahoma, to these places, forced to leave, forced to do these things.

00:08:08.736 --> 00:08:18.613
It's pain beyond anybody's comprehension, if it was mine. And I'm not going to say here, "Well, I can relate, I can do all this."No, no, no.

00:08:18.614 --> 00:08:26.166
I saw a glimpse. It's like opening up a book and you see it, and you open it up, you get a glimpse of something.

00:08:26.167 --> 00:08:31.882
But it's that way in the spirit. I got a glimpse of something, something that was very hurtful.

00:08:31.883 --> 00:08:46.239
And me as a white guy, I, like I said, I don't know why He chose me, but I am humbled, and I know what the Lord said.

00:08:46.240 --> 00:08:51.960
He said, "I've not forgotten your prayers,"and I've heard that echo inside of my spirit.

00:08:51.961 --> 00:09:04.512
And I could see the prayers coming up from those African slaves in those camps with these wood huts, and they had little fires, and they were looking at the stars and they were looking at the North.

00:09:04.513 --> 00:09:10.479
And it was interesting because that Tubman lady, it was about the North Star. I could see the North Star. I could see the Big Dipper.

00:09:10.480 --> 00:09:16.323
I could see they were navigating by stars at night to get through because they didn't travel in the day.

00:09:16.324 --> 00:09:22.723
So, they were trying to get through in the nighttime and they were using the stars as a map so they wouldn't get lost.

00:09:22.724 --> 00:09:27.688
And that's what I was seeing in the spirit. But they were looking for the North Star.

00:09:27.689 --> 00:09:33.980
And I thought that was really interesting because that's how detailed these visions were last night.

00:09:33.981 --> 00:09:53.773
I could see them, and they had little bitty fire torches, and they were trying to move through areas, and I was like, "What in the world, Lord?"And as I'm looking and able to look over there, I see them praying and singing old songs.

00:09:53.774 --> 00:10:06.091
And there were old—not Pentecostal songs, but old Bible songs like hymnals, old hymns, old songs that we don't sing anymore.

00:10:06.092 --> 00:10:15.679
I was trying to listen because I was hearing, and this is what's amazing: I've never been in a vision and heard people singing before.

00:10:15.680 --> 00:10:29.571
I could hear the African-American people singing, the women and the men, and it was a deep, heavy song.

00:10:29.572 --> 00:10:38.182
It wasn't joyful. It was heavy, like groanings in the spirit.

00:10:38.183 --> 00:10:44.631
It was heavy, asking the Father for freedom. "Where are you? Why have you forgotten us?

00:10:44.632 --> 00:10:59.412
Why are we going through this?"crying out for the Father to redeem them and set them free. And as I saw them praying, I saw a man named Abraham Lincoln.

00:10:59.413 --> 00:11:13.439
And God raised up a man named Abraham Lincoln to do what he did to bring freedom to the slaves. And I saw them murder him.

00:11:13.440 --> 00:11:25.870
I saw all this stuff panned out, and he was a really tall man, and some people say, "Well, he was 6'4","but with his top hat—I saw his hat, and it made him look like he was a lot bigger.

00:11:25.871 --> 00:11:31.329
I'm telling you in the vision—and this is another thing—was everybody else a lot smaller?

00:11:31.330 --> 00:11:37.356
Because he looked like he was head and shoulders above everybody, from these men that were below him.

00:11:37.357 --> 00:11:40.106
So I'm like, well, maybe people weren't very tall back then.

00:11:40.107 --> 00:11:48.926
I don't know, because when I saw him, he was like a really big guy in this black suit in the vision, and I'm still trying to figure out what I saw.

00:11:48.927 --> 00:11:57.672
I'm like, was he standing next to kids? I don't know. All I know is I tell you these things, but I saw he was a lot bigger of a man than everybody else was.

00:11:57.673 --> 00:12:01.992
So maybe everybody else is like 5'5"or something. I don't know.

00:12:01.993 --> 00:12:10.620
They didn't look like they were very big people. Does it matter? No. I just try to figure it out.

00:12:10.621 --> 00:12:15.219
I love when the Lord shows me things, and I take it very seriously.

00:12:15.220 --> 00:12:29.060
It's His love language towards me. It's intimacy. It's how I learn how to communicate with Him. And He shows me things.

00:12:29.061 --> 00:12:42.402
And it's something that I never thought I would ever go public about to the point like I am now, that 70,000 people would look at it a day.

00:12:42.403 --> 00:12:47.039
But I know a lot of you are just desperate and want intimacy with Him.

00:12:47.040 --> 00:12:53.658
That's why you're here. You want your own relationship. And the Lord wants you to have it.

00:12:53.659 --> 00:13:04.357
He's no respecter of persons, but He is a respecter of those that seek Him. And I want to tell you, as you seek Him, you'll find Him.

00:13:04.358 --> 00:13:17.553
But when He told me He was going to bring a restitution—restitution, but with interest.

00:13:17.554 --> 00:13:26.712
With interest. And people say, 'Well, how's that going to happen?'I don't know. It's in the spirit.

00:13:26.713 --> 00:13:37.313
And if God said He would reward those and bring that to them, you can take it to the bank. My Father is able.

00:13:37.314 --> 00:13:56.624
I'm not going to question the God of the universe, the God of everything, and go, 'Well, how are you going to do that with my peanut brain?'when He can make manna out of nothing, turn the water into wine, do all the things that He's always done, and do super exceedingly abundantly above all that you dare ask or think.

00:13:56.625 --> 00:14:09.553
If He said He would do it, He's able, and I don't question it. I just go, He told me to tell you for you to believe for it.

00:14:09.554 --> 00:14:22.048
And those of you that are in the young generation, if those others have gone home—your elders have gone home, because I saw 80 years old, 90 years old, and I didn't know why I was seeing that.

00:14:22.049 --> 00:14:30.609
But if you were a child in the 1921 race riots, you'd still be here probably, right?

00:14:30.610 --> 00:14:38.111
That's only 104 years ago. Yeah. So if you were a child, you're still here probably, right?

00:14:38.112 --> 00:14:45.859
No, well, no, to be born, they'd probably be dead. Yeah, if possible.

00:14:45.860 --> 00:14:53.759
I mean, they're like 106, 107. It's very, very unlikely. Pretty rare.

00:14:53.760 --> 00:14:59.679
Very unlikely. So, it's their grandchildren. Yeah. It would be their grandchild or their children.

00:14:59.680 --> 00:15:04.518
Their children would probably still be here. They were raised still up underneath that.

00:15:04.519 --> 00:15:09.743
They're old, though. That would be the 80 and 90 years old probably that I was seeing in the spirit realm.

00:15:09.744 --> 00:15:18.911
The Lord was showing me that He was still bringing restitution for them. Right. So, wow. It's just time goes.

00:15:18.912 --> 00:15:28.504
But after I see what the Lord is showing me, for you to believe just like it was for Diana to believe for her ancestors—ancestors, they didn't get the restitution.

00:15:28.505 --> 00:15:33.274
You know, they get Indian land, tribal benefits, and things like that.

00:15:33.274 --> 00:15:42.822
And but the Lord was showing me making the wrong right, making the wrong right, that He had not forgotten it.

00:15:42.823 --> 00:15:47.515
And it's not brushed underneath the rug. It's time to take the rug off.

00:15:47.516 --> 00:15:55.136
And the white folks, I realize there's a lot more ignorant people than what you think.

00:15:55.137 --> 00:16:01.631
It's like Diana, and I told her we got some dumb emails, but you know what, people are...

00:16:01.632 --> 00:16:14.324
it's the devil behind them. They don't understand. They're blinded by their own religious Pharisee, racist, bigoted ways.

00:16:14.325 --> 00:16:23.106
And that's what it is. I use these hard words, but my goodness, folks, we have some really ignorant people.

00:16:23.107 --> 00:16:34.935
And you go, 'Okay, I'm not inciting any kind of violence. I'm not inciting people to get upset.'I'm trying to tell you the Father wants to restore you.

00:16:34.936 --> 00:16:39.870
The Father wants to restore you. And that's all it's about with me.

00:16:39.871 --> 00:16:45.352
I'm obedient unto Him unto death. And when He says speak, I speak.

00:16:45.353 --> 00:16:53.238
And this is what the Spirit of the Lord wanted to say to you yesterday: that He loves you, and He's not forgotten you.

00:16:53.239 --> 00:16:59.790
And the pain of the past, He's going to give you back more than what you ever... it's more than sevenfold.

00:16:59.791 --> 00:17:12.401
He said, 'I'm going to restore back all the money.'So 400 years of wealth, if you'll believe for it.

00:17:12.402 --> 00:17:28.553
400 years of family bloodline back pay with interest. And I was like, that's millions of dollars in my opinion.

00:17:28.554 --> 00:17:41.906
I mean, so believe God for big. Believe God for big. Why not? If He said He would do it, believe for it.

00:17:41.907 --> 00:17:47.719
And so that was what I had for you today of that, just rehearsing things.

00:17:47.720 --> 00:18:03.608
Now, side note, that was precious in itself, but the things I'm seeing about Israel and the baby wrapped in the blanket with Israel, I don't understand all that.

00:18:03.609 --> 00:18:09.457
A rebirthing, new things are going to take place. So, what a patriotism.

00:18:09.457 --> 00:18:19.705
There's something about patriotism from June, this next month today, going all the way into July—of patriotism.

00:18:19.706 --> 00:18:30.285
There's something, and people say, 'You say what's going to happen in 24 hours.'Everything will change within a 24-hour period whenever you'll see it.

00:18:30.286 --> 00:18:36.235
I don't know. That's just... I just hear this, and I am like an antenna.

00:18:36.236 --> 00:18:39.337
I have my little antenna up and you're picking up from the receiver.

00:18:39.338 --> 00:18:48.510
I have my receiver, and I have the main broadcast going on, and my little antenna is going beep-beep like my little radio, and I'm picking up my radio, my Bible.

00:18:48.511 --> 00:18:59.090
And I got this, and it's downloaded into me that God says that everything you know is going to change within a 24-hour period.

00:18:59.091 --> 00:19:10.702
And I hear that and I go, I'm relaying it back as, 'This is what the Spirit of the Lord tells me to tell you.'And everything's going to change within a 24-hour period.

00:19:10.703 --> 00:19:19.860
Everything you know—a great shaking to awaken is coming. A great shaking to awaken is coming.

00:19:19.861 --> 00:19:26.239
I saw a great war breaking out with Israel and Iran in the days ahead.

00:19:26.240 --> 00:19:48.140
And I told you back in January that I saw an American missile striking a mountain that was an underground city, and Iran set all kinds of deterrents trying to stop this missile.

00:19:48.141 --> 00:20:05.086
It was a very powerful one. But when Israel does this, I saw that they set Iran back financially, globally, nuclearly, everything. They put them back in the Stone Age.

00:20:05.087 --> 00:20:18.645
I heard the Spirit of the Lord say, 'They put them back in the Stone Age.'But when they do this, they strike their oil and their gasoline plants, their petroleum plants, right?

00:20:18.646 --> 00:20:23.757
I saw like gas, I saw, you know, these refineries. Thank you, Holy Spirit.

00:20:23.758 --> 00:20:29.249
I'm trying, y'all, because, I'm telling you, these names and these big names, I don't use them.

00:20:29.250 --> 00:20:38.737
Refineries. I saw refineries. And when they strike the refineries, I saw gas and oil prices skyrocketing.

00:20:38.738 --> 00:20:50.112
I've warned you of this since 2023, about this for a season, for a season.

00:20:50.113 --> 00:21:04.066
And then the Lord showed me in that vision the 1970 gas wars. I saw cars lined up down the blocks because of gas shortages.

00:21:04.067 --> 00:21:10.521
Now, if that still happens, I don't know, but this is what I saw. This is in 2023.

00:21:10.522 --> 00:21:21.754
And the Lord told me at this time that gas would skyrocket, and it would bring the price of oil up really high, really high.

00:21:21.755 --> 00:21:32.845
I saw it going up to $200 a barrel, like big money trying to flow, which would stimulate the American economy.

00:21:32.846 --> 00:21:40.959
It stimulated the American economy whenever these big oil productions get hit in the Middle East.

00:21:40.960 --> 00:21:46.758
And it would happen for a season, for a window. I don't know how long, for a window.

00:21:46.759 --> 00:21:56.055
And I saw gas in the Mediterranean being drilled. I saw the Gulf of—people want to argue America—Gulf of Mexico.

00:21:56.056 --> 00:22:00.794
I don't care. Call it what you want. They were drilling, drilling, drilling, drilling.

00:22:00.795 --> 00:22:09.560
And I saw, "drill, baby, drill."I saw pipelines being opened up, being worked out, making big agreements for pipelines.

00:22:09.561 --> 00:22:14.189
The Nord Stream pipeline, I believe, is what it's called. It was the big pipeline.

00:22:14.190 --> 00:22:29.199
I saw it being talked about and opened up, working on it, just trying to get this pipe deal going, doing major oil big deals ahead, stimulating America's economy.

00:22:29.200 --> 00:22:41.032
But when this happens, I saw great antisemitism because of people being mad at Israel about what they're about to do.

00:22:41.033 --> 00:22:53.839
Remember this. I saw them wanting to retaliate with war: Russia, Syria, Turkey.

00:22:53.840 --> 00:22:59.678
I saw them getting upset, and the Middle East, against, "Well, you did all that.

00:22:59.679 --> 00:23:03.888
We're going to come after you."So, will we see all this in the days ahead?

00:23:03.889 --> 00:23:07.999
I don't know, folks. All I know is these are visions that I've seen.

00:23:08.000 --> 00:23:15.485
Have we changed it through prayer? I don't believe we have. We hear some of this on the news now.

00:23:15.486 --> 00:23:24.386
Some of the things that I see take years to come to pass. Sometimes it takes 10 years, you know, I don't know.

00:23:24.387 --> 00:23:30.335
Sometimes it's months. So, let's pray for President Trump.

00:23:30.336 --> 00:23:41.190
Remember I told you I kept hearing him say, "I want to go about this..."I told you in January, I said he said, "I want to go about this diplomatically.

00:23:41.191 --> 00:23:47.995
I'm not pushing the button. I'm not pushing the button, but Israel did it anyway."Remember?

00:23:47.996 --> 00:23:57.268
But then I've been praying and I've told you all I see a black swan event. We got to create a boogeyman.

00:23:57.269 --> 00:24:02.655
I hear him say we have to create an enemy so that it justifies our reaction.

00:24:02.656 --> 00:24:07.856
We're going to have to retaliate and make... We have a ripe cause.

00:24:07.857 --> 00:24:13.038
Like, you know they're bad. We have to stop these bad people, right?

00:24:13.039 --> 00:24:18.759
But all of it was about nuclear power, about oil, about a lot of things.

00:24:18.760 --> 00:24:27.839
So, just what I've seen, you take it for what it's worth. I mean, it's a lot to us, right? Yes.

00:24:27.840 --> 00:24:35.483
And we pray over it and I take everything the Lord shows me to prayer every single time, and I intercede over it, and this is my job.

00:24:35.484 --> 00:24:39.725
You're just a part of it now. It's very public, but it's what we do.

00:24:39.726 --> 00:24:45.510
I've been doing it, like I said, for a long time. My whole marriage. Yes, for sure.

00:24:45.511 --> 00:24:49.429
This is what we do, and we take notes and we write down what the Lord tells us.

00:24:49.430 --> 00:24:56.774
And that's why it's become so big. It wasn't like this at first.

00:24:56.775 --> 00:25:02.086
It's taken development, and he would show me glimpses of things.

00:25:02.087 --> 00:25:10.258
And as I've been faithful with little, he gives me more and more and more. And now it's really cool because whenever I get close to...

00:25:10.259 --> 00:25:14.319
Like, if we're believing for something and Diana says, "I need you to pray for me.

00:25:14.320 --> 00:25:18.416
I'm overcoming a headache or something,"you know, I don't know, I just give her an instance.

00:25:18.417 --> 00:25:30.158
I can touch her now, or she can, or I can my kids, and the Lord will show me exactly what's going on and how to fix it, what to pray, everything.

00:25:30.159 --> 00:25:34.749
And that's part of the healing part. And it's developing and developing and developing.

00:25:34.750 --> 00:25:43.038
And it's very interesting. But I just told you something I don't ever talk about, but it's very interesting.

00:25:43.039 --> 00:25:58.613
Amazing. The root cause, everything, where it stems from, how it got there, things like that, with people.

00:25:58.614 --> 00:26:04.522
And it's all glory to God, folks, because I am nothing without him.

00:26:04.523 --> 00:26:15.182
It's all about Jesus and what he's done, and he gives us gifts to walk in. I'm nothing special. I'm just Brandon.

00:26:15.183 --> 00:26:22.874
I'm just grateful that everybody would want to show up every single day and want to pray with me. Thank you. And there are some people so kind.

00:26:22.875 --> 00:26:40.418
It's like one dear sister, "Hey, if everybody gives them a dollar, if everybody gives them a dollar, you can stop eBay and Poshmark."And I told Diana, I said, "Our people are kind, such good hearts."We thought about doing a book thing.

00:26:40.419 --> 00:26:45.532
Diana and I pray about doing books; we pray about doing all these things.

00:26:45.533 --> 00:26:58.863
But she said, even in the car, she said, "Brandon, even if I did a book deal, I could write a book, Brandon, but we are such givers that even if we did it, most people...

00:26:58.864 --> 00:27:04.820
You see these big ministries, everybody writes a book about every year, and they sell them for $25 a piece.

00:27:04.821 --> 00:27:08.140
And if they sell 100,000 copies of those, that's a lot of money.

00:27:08.141 --> 00:27:14.989
You know, they're making millions."And so our heart is, immediately, we just want to give everything away.

00:27:14.990 --> 00:27:24.424
And so she's like, "Even if I wrote the book, we would put all our finances into making a book and we would give it all away, Brandon,"she goes, "because it would be hard.

00:27:24.425 --> 00:27:36.752
It would bother me to sell a book for 25 bucks, unless the Lord told us to do it to fund our ministry."But my heart is to give, because freely I have received, freely I give.

00:27:36.753 --> 00:27:49.439
I just... Books, tapes, CDs. I would wait for days, weeks, save up my money to be able to buy a tape series whenever a special guest speaker came to church.

00:27:49.440 --> 00:27:56.457
And I would go, "Oh, Diana, can we use our tithes to buy those this month?"Because that was our treat. That was our treat.

00:27:56.457 --> 00:28:03.655
